s/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嘩屌 娘到一個點<br />\n<br />\n4. 雖然知佢係美國電影 但哩套嘅大美國英雄主義 同埋過份歌頌美國嘅情懷 真係有啲嘔心 尤其最後嗰句咩 「因為老子就是美國總統！」WTF<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然係馬後炮 但如果個故事變成美國總統真係背後策劃人 為權力而表面做好人 但暗中搵人阻止男主角 整幾條伏線指向其他角色屈鳩佢哋做反角 而女主角同女船長係總統後後嘅間諜咁 可能會好睇啲<br />\n<br />\nsor 可能太認真 但我真心覺得佢曬咗個idea"},{"pid":"b046a8ed6807fcf57c64b8d789ff2a8b0edf898b","tid":460164,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T13:50:58.000Z","msg":"辣辣咩嚟"},{"pid":"23988559e887dcd5d9cc2ca5e298a32b74dac3a1","tid":460164,"uid":80736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T13:51:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>辣辣咩嚟</blockquote><br />\n？"},{"pid":"7adfc82a0f46e7927007235c65901e3ff82cae96","tid":460164,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T13:56:21.000Z","msg":"勁鍾意食豬皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cd28827de63406a4cf50b26f97955dbee2e9c1d","tid":460164,"uid":80736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T13:58:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>勁鍾意食豬皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為平，所以特別多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}